A Change Of Pace - Prepare For The Masses (2006)

Prepare the Masses is the second album by pop punk band A Change of Pace. It was released on the August 15, 2006. The album doesn't contain screaming lyrics as in the previous album, An Offer You Can't Refuse, and is considered to be more pop punk with little hardcore influence.

